Somewhere in space, a stasis pod is headed straight Earth. It enters the 
atmosphere and crash lands on the outskirts of the main Predacon base. The 
computer scans his surroundings, checking for intelligent life. It picks up 
some fossils to the west. The computer then scans them and morphs the 
protoform to match the fossils. The stasis pod opens and a new bot is online!
